The,GitHub,Issues,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,GitHub,activity,events,services,into,their,applications,gaining,access,to,authenticated,users,visible,repositories,to,list,get,and,or,edit,an,issue,This,API,requires,two,factor,authentication,GitHub,is,one,of,the,software,providers,that,specialize,in,a,wide,range,of,application,development